data.description: Freshly Painted Exterior 10/23! Newer A/C Unit! Enjoy owning this adorable 3-bed, 2-bath home in Tucson! This fully fenced property offers carport space, no-fuss front yard, and a cozy front patio. Once inside, you'll immediately be welcomed by the inviting living room filled with plenty of natural light and features wood-look tile flooring throughout. Spotless eat-in kitchen comes with a handy pantry, stainless steel appliances, track lighting, elegant cabinetry, granite counters, and mosaic backsplash. All sizable bedrooms include bi-folding closets and ceiling fans. The primary bedroom provides a private bathroom for added comfort. In the spacious backyard, you'll find a convenient storage shed and a lovely gazebo perfect for entertaining. This value won't disappoint!
